Class ClientBean

java.lang.Object
  org.jdesktop.application.AbstractBean
      au.gov.sbr.core.client.beans.BeanBase
          au.gov.sbr.core.client.beans.ClientBean
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class ClientBean
extends BeanBase

This bean represents the client application's main window and all the properties that are exposed to the GUI for binding.
